<%- layout('../layouts/layout') %>
<main class="container-fluid">
    <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <i class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <strong>DISCLAIMER:</strong>
        Though you can play this game on mobile phones, I do not recommended it. The game is best enjoyed on a desktop. Use a
        tablet at the vary least.
    </div>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <h1><%- title %></h1>
            <p>Welcome to the <%- title %></p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="game">
                Play Now
                <i class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <section class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-body">
            <h1>About</h1><!--TODO: Fill in About Section-->
            <hr>
            <p>
                A NodeJS game made as part of the Floatplane Media hiring process.
            </p>
            <p>
            You can find the LTT post about it <span style="text-decoration: line-through">here</span> (Not making one until I hear back from Floatplane)
            </p>
            <p>
            You can find a live version [here](https://infinite-brook-45557.herokuapp.com/)
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-body">
            <h1>How To Play</h1><!--TODO: Fill in How To Play Section-->
            <hr>
            <ul>
                <li>Use the <kbd>&uparrow;</kbd> or <kbd>W</kbd> key to go up a lane.</li>
                <li>Use the <kbd>&downarrow;</kbd> or <kbd>S</kbd> key to go down a lane.</li>
                <li>You can also tap the top or bottom of the road to move up or down by one lane.</li>
                <li>
                    Pick up coins to increase your score.
                    <ul>
                        <li>Team Red coins award 100 points.</li>
                        <li>Team Green coins award 250 points.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Avoid flaming servers.
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            No, they are NOT the same ones as in Linus's server room.
                            <ul>
                                <li><small>(I'm trying not to incur the wrath of Linus)</small></li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
